24
00:01:55,694 --> 00:01:57,664
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The race is on the 15th,</b></font>

25
00:01:57,664 --> 00:02:01,034
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>so we still have one more week.</b></font>

26
00:02:01,034 --> 00:02:04,034
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's a good thing it's not tomorrow.</b></font>

27
00:02:04,034 --> 00:02:09,374
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Aren't the Red Suns and the
Night Kids racing tomorrow?</b></font>

28
00:02:09,374 --> 00:02:10,844
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That's it!</b></font>

29
00:02:10,844 --> 00:02:15,014
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Take Takumi there and
make him watch their race!</b></font>

30
00:02:15,014 --> 00:02:17,184
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It could be exciting enough</b></font>

31
00:02:17,184 --> 00:02:20,044
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>to snap him out of his daydreaming!</b></font>

32
00:02:20,044 --> 00:02:24,084
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That's a good idea. That should do the trick!</b></font>

33
00:02:24,084 --> 00:02:28,184
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>He'll have a rude awakening.</b></font>

34
00:02:32,564 --> 00:02:37,864
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="66"><b>{\an5}"Act 22: Fierce Uphill Battle!"</b></font>

35
00:02:49,074 --> 00:02:52,014
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Hey, Dad, I've been thinking...</b></font>

36
00:02:52,014 --> 00:02:53,884
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>About what?</b></font>

37
00:02:53,884 --> 00:02:58,524
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I raced at Usui Pass the other night.</b></font>

38
00:02:58,524 --> 00:03:02,784
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I thought it would be totally
different from Akina Pass.</b></font>

39
00:03:05,764 --> 00:03:09,434
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>But as I drove it...</b></font>

40
00:03:09,434 --> 00:03:12,804
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>...I realized that it felt very similar to Akina.</b></font>

41
00:03:14,874 --> 00:03:16,434
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Very good.</b></font>

42
00:03:16,434 --> 00:03:17,874
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Is it?</b></font>

43
00:03:17,874 --> 00:03:21,744
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Usui is a completely
different course from Akina,</b></font>

44
00:03:21,744 --> 00:03:25,714
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>but you ran your usual race on it.</b></font>

45
00:03:25,714 --> 00:03:30,154
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's about how much "Akina"
you take with you to other courses.</b></font>

46
00:03:32,424 --> 00:03:35,114
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>--Good luck with the deliveries.
--Okay.</b></font>

47
00:03:55,644 --> 00:03:59,274
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>How much "Akina"I take with me...</i></b></font>

48
00:04:08,154 --> 00:04:12,494
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I think I sort of understand</i>
<i>what he's trying to say.</i></b></font>

49
00:04:29,374 --> 00:04:31,504
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I need a nap.</b></font>

50
00:04:32,614 --> 00:04:35,384
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>He's completely lost in a daydream.</b></font>

51
00:04:35,384 --> 00:04:38,654
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Okay, let the operation begin!</b></font>

52
00:04:38,654 --> 00:04:42,394
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Hey, Takumi!</b></font>

53
00:04:42,394 --> 00:04:45,064
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Big news! Don't freak out!</b></font>

54
00:04:45,064 --> 00:04:49,664
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The Red Suns and the Night Kids
are battling it out tonight!</b></font>

55
00:04:49,664 --> 00:04:53,834
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>--So?
--What do you mean, "so"?!</b></font>

56
00:04:53,834 --> 00:04:57,004
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Since you're taking on
Ryosuke Takahashi next week,</b></font>

57
00:04:57,004 --> 00:05:00,374
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>this race is a must-see!</b></font>

58
00:05:00,374 --> 00:05:02,214
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Okay, then!</b></font>

59
00:05:02,214 --> 00:05:07,554
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Let's take your Eight-Six, since it's a
waste of gas to drive two cars there.</b></font>

60
00:05:07,554 --> 00:05:11,024
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>--Mine?
--I'm getting fired up!</b></font>

61
00:05:11,024 --> 00:05:14,194
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You're excited too, right?</b></font>

62
00:05:14,194 --> 00:05:15,394
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Right...</b></font>

63
00:05:15,394 --> 00:05:18,224
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'll meet you at your place at 7:00.</b></font>

64
00:05:18,224 --> 00:05:20,994
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Don't forget to borrow the Eight-Six!</b></font>

65
00:05:38,184 --> 00:05:40,684
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The crowd is huge.</b></font>

66
00:05:40,684 --> 00:05:42,854
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Are Takumi and Itsuki here?</b></font>

67
00:05:42,854 --> 00:05:45,584
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Not yet.</b></font>

68
00:05:45,584 --> 00:05:50,194
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I sure hope Itsuki was able to pull this off.</b></font>

69
00:05:50,194 --> 00:05:54,034
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Hurry up, Takumi, or we'll miss the race.</b></font>

70
00:05:54,034 --> 00:05:58,364
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>We got lost because you didn't
want to take the toll road.</b></font>

71
00:05:58,364 --> 00:06:00,534
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You're too cheap.</b></font>

72
00:06:00,534 --> 00:06:01,874
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Look who's talking.</b></font>

73
00:06:01,874 --> 00:06:06,374
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You're the one who didn't drive to save on gas.</b></font>

74
00:06:06,374 --> 00:06:09,474
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I've never heard of a racer
with no sense of direction...</b></font>

75
00:06:11,144 --> 00:06:14,154
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>This must be a side effect of his daydreaming.</i></b></font>

76
00:06:14,154 --> 00:06:16,244
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I got it.</b></font>

77
00:06:17,154 --> 00:06:19,784
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>We really gotta hurry!</b></font>

78
00:06:33,404 --> 00:06:35,834
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You made me wait.</b></font>

79
00:06:35,834 --> 00:06:38,974
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The main character shows up last.</b></font>

80
00:06:38,974 --> 00:06:43,644
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Myogi's ravine is steep, so try not to die.</b></font>

81
00:06:43,644 --> 00:06:46,814
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Enough. Your hands are shaking.</b></font>

82
00:06:46,814 --> 00:06:51,624
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Don't worry, it'll be quick.
No Night Kid can touch me.</b></font>

83
00:06:51,624 --> 00:06:56,114
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Your arrogance could end your life.</b></font>

84
00:07:00,094 --> 00:07:02,464
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Let's go, before the rain starts.</b></font>

85
00:07:02,464 --> 00:07:04,504
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>--Yeah.
--An Eight-Six!</b></font>

86
00:07:04,504 --> 00:07:06,764
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Akina's Eight-Six came!</b></font>

87
00:07:09,104 --> 00:07:10,934
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>An Eight-Six?</i></b></font>

88
00:07:19,284 --> 00:07:22,714
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Check out this huge crowd!</b></font>

89
00:07:22,714 --> 00:07:25,724
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Just concentrate on finding them, okay?</b></font>

90
00:07:25,724 --> 00:07:27,624
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I know...</b></font>

91
00:07:27,624 --> 00:07:30,794
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>...but it's hard to spot them in this crowd.</b></font>

92
00:07:30,794 --> 00:07:33,524
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Where should we park?</b></font>

93
00:07:33,524 --> 00:07:35,534
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What about the top?</b></font>

94
00:07:35,534 --> 00:07:37,364
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>There's a big parking lot.</b></font>

95
00:07:37,364 --> 00:07:40,304
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>All right, let's go up, then.</b></font>

96
00:07:47,004 --> 00:07:49,544
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I knew you'd come.</i></b></font>

97
00:07:49,544 --> 00:07:51,584
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>You're getting me fired up.</i></b></font>

98
00:07:51,584 --> 00:07:56,414
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Eight-Six, I'll show you</i>
<i>how much I've improved.</i></b></font>

99
00:08:00,224 --> 00:08:02,024
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>--An Eight-Six!
--You mean Akina's?</b></font>

100
00:08:02,024 --> 00:08:04,424
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>--Yeah.
--Is it really?</b></font>

101
00:08:06,094 --> 00:08:09,034
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Hey Takumi, is it just me,</b></font>

102
00:08:09,034 --> 00:08:12,504
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>or do you think people are looking at us?</b></font>

103
00:08:12,504 --> 00:08:15,234
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>--Yeah.
--What do you mean, "yeah"?!</b></font>

104
00:08:15,234 --> 00:08:18,274
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>They totally recognize us.</b></font>

105
00:08:18,274 --> 00:08:21,844
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Akina's Eight-Six is famous now.</b></font>

106
00:08:21,844 --> 00:08:25,514
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>They have their eye on you, you know?</b></font>

107
00:08:25,514 --> 00:08:28,614
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It was a good idea to drive the Eight-Six here.</b></font>

108
00:08:28,614 --> 00:08:30,884
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What are you muttering about?</b></font>

109
00:08:32,024 --> 00:08:34,594
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Okay, come forward!</b></font>

110
00:08:34,594 --> 00:08:36,554
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Forward!</b></font>

111
00:08:44,464 --> 00:08:47,874
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Okay. The road is clear!</b></font>

112
00:08:47,874 --> 00:08:49,204
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'll count down!</b></font>

113
00:08:49,204 --> 00:08:51,274
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Five... Four...</b></font>

114
00:08:51,274 --> 00:08:53,444
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Three... Two...</b></font>

115
00:08:53,444 --> 00:08:55,574
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>One... Go!</b></font>

116
00:09:04,824 --> 00:09:07,594
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Wow! What a fast start!</b></font>

117
00:09:07,594 --> 00:09:11,324
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I know Keisuke will win.</i></b></font>

118
00:09:11,324 --> 00:09:16,064
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Don't lose. It's not an option on our turf.</i></b></font>

119
00:09:19,504 --> 00:09:20,934
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="66"><b>{\an5}"Takahashi"</b></font>

120
00:09:22,774 --> 00:09:24,674
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's started.</b></font>

121
00:09:26,744 --> 00:09:28,404
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Rain...</i></b></font>

122
00:09:29,844 --> 00:09:33,514
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>The FD's best weapon is</i>
<i>its high cornering speed.</i></b></font>

123
00:09:33,514 --> 00:09:36,284
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Don't forget that, Keisuke.</i></b></font>

124
00:09:41,324 --> 00:09:42,694
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Takumi?</b></font>

125
00:09:42,694 --> 00:09:46,524
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Don't you think Myogi Pass
is similar to Akina Pass?</b></font>

126
00:09:46,524 --> 00:09:47,864
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I don't know.</b></font>

127
00:09:47,864 --> 00:09:51,334
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It seems more like Usui Pass to me.</b></font>

128
00:09:51,334 --> 00:09:54,204
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's nothing like Usui!</b></font>

129
00:09:54,204 --> 00:09:58,864
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>It's no use. He's totally lost,</i>
<i>out in the deepest sea.</i></b></font>

130
00:10:00,104 --> 00:10:02,514
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Take a good look at it!</b></font>

131
00:10:02,514 --> 00:10:04,314
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's not as narrow as Usui,</b></font>

132
00:10:04,314 --> 00:10:08,854
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>and this uphill is just like Akina's.</b></font>

133
00:10:08,854 --> 00:10:12,484
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I mean the rhythm is similar.</b></font>

134
00:10:12,484 --> 00:10:14,824
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Rhythm...?</b></font>

135
00:10:42,654 --> 00:10:46,354
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Be careful! An FD is quick around corners.</i></b></font>

136
00:10:46,354 --> 00:10:51,354
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I never thought anyone could</i>
<i>follow me up Myogi's hill.</i></b></font>

137
00:10:55,864 --> 00:10:58,234
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>He's starting to abuse the steering.</i></b></font>

138
00:10:58,234 --> 00:11:00,704
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>He's trying to speed away.</i></b></font>

139
00:11:00,704 --> 00:11:05,334
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>If he did that on a downhill,</i>
<i>the tires would compress.</i></b></font>

140
00:11:55,494 --> 00:11:56,824
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>They just passed the mid-point.</b></font>

141
00:11:56,824 --> 00:11:59,294
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The R32 is in front...</b></font>

142
00:11:59,294 --> 00:12:02,894
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>...but it's very close.</b></font>

143
00:12:02,894 --> 00:12:04,404
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I see.</b></font>

144
00:12:04,404 --> 00:12:06,164
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Tell me one thing...</b></font>

145
00:12:06,164 --> 00:12:10,174
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>How did Keisuke look coming out of the turn?</b></font>

146
00:12:10,174 --> 00:12:13,844
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>He was one step slower than Nakazato,</b></font>

147
00:12:13,844 --> 00:12:18,114
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>but overall, he seems under
control and very smooth,</b></font>

148
00:12:18,114 --> 00:12:22,984
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>unlike Nakazato's aggressive
but inconsistent run.</b></font>

149
00:12:22,984 --> 00:12:26,014
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I got it. Thanks.</b></font>

150
00:12:27,184 --> 00:12:32,464
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>You've improved, Keisuke,</i>
<i>to be able to race like that.</i></b></font>

151
00:12:32,464 --> 00:12:36,464
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The R32 is in front. Very tight!</b></font>

152
00:12:36,464 --> 00:12:41,304
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>They just passed me.
Nakazato is barely in front.</b></font>

153
00:12:41,304 --> 00:12:44,144
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It sounds like Takeshi is doing well.</b></font>

154
00:12:44,144 --> 00:12:47,004
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>He's been training hard.</b></font>

155
00:12:47,004 --> 00:12:51,544
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>He became a different person
after losing to the Eight-Six.</b></font>

156
00:12:51,544 --> 00:12:57,854
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I've always considered Takeshi</i>
<i>to be my enemy. But now...</i></b></font>

157
00:12:57,854 --> 00:13:03,954
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Knowing that he's fighting for</i>
<i>our pride, I feel the camaraderie.</i></b></font>

158
00:13:03,954 --> 00:13:06,484
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I've never felt this way before.</i></b></font>

159
00:13:07,894 --> 00:13:10,804
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The R32's in the lead!</b></font>

160
00:13:10,804 --> 00:13:14,494
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Win, Takeshi! I'm counting on you!</b></font>

161
00:13:20,004 --> 00:13:24,414
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I can hear the squeals, but I can't see them.</b></font>

162
00:13:25,684 --> 00:13:27,414
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What?</b></font>

163
00:13:27,414 --> 00:13:29,074
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Rain...</b></font>

164
00:13:32,924 --> 00:13:35,994
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Oh, no! They're battling at full speed!</b></font>

165
00:13:35,994 --> 00:13:38,764
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's most dangerous
when it first starts raining.</b></font>

166
00:13:38,764 --> 00:13:43,434
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The rain lifts up the dirt and oil on
the surface and makes it slippery.</b></font>

167
00:13:43,434 --> 00:13:45,664
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>They could easily crash.</b></font>

168
00:13:56,444 --> 00:13:58,284
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Raindrops...</i></b></font>

169
00:13:58,284 --> 00:14:01,184
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Darn, couldn't it have waited?</i></b></font>

170
00:14:01,184 --> 00:14:03,384
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I gotta be alert.</i></b></font>

171
00:14:03,384 --> 00:14:06,714
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I could lose control without warning.</i></b></font>

172
00:14:37,924 --> 00:14:40,384
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's really coming down.</b></font>

173
00:14:40,384 --> 00:14:43,384
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I hope they don't stop the race.</b></font>

174
00:14:44,464 --> 00:14:47,064
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>--Hey, Itsuki?
--Yeah?</b></font>

175
00:14:47,064 --> 00:14:51,264
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Since that's the finish line,
this must be the last corner, right?</b></font>

176
00:14:51,264 --> 00:14:53,334
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Yeah.</b></font>

177
00:14:53,334 --> 00:14:56,834
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That's the highest point in Myogi Pass,</b></font>

178
00:14:56,834 --> 00:15:00,174
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>so this is a downhill corner.</b></font>

179
00:15:00,174 --> 00:15:02,334
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The only downhill corner.</b></font>

180
00:15:03,644 --> 00:15:05,514
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Here they come!</b></font>

181
00:15:27,634 --> 00:15:30,174
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>This is it!</i></b></font>

182
00:15:30,174 --> 00:15:35,704
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>That's suicidal! You'll crash</i>
<i>into the wall at that speed!</i></b></font>

183
00:15:42,984 --> 00:15:45,154
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I know I can do this!</i></b></font>

184
00:15:45,154 --> 00:15:48,144
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>My FD's telling me I can!</i></b></font>

185
00:15:55,994 --> 00:15:58,694
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>They're coming at us!</b></font>

186
00:16:21,354 --> 00:16:23,014
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The FD won!</b></font>

187
00:16:26,094 --> 00:16:28,264
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'm so impressed!</b></font>

188
00:16:28,264 --> 00:16:31,564
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Man, Keisuke Takahashi is good!</b></font>

189
00:16:31,564 --> 00:16:37,404
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>This is the first time that I</i>
<i>was inspired by other racers.</i></b></font>

190
00:16:37,404 --> 00:16:42,574
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Seeing a great race like</i>
<i>that makes me restless.</i></b></font>

191
00:16:47,114 --> 00:16:50,284
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You got lucky, Keisuke Takahashi.</b></font>

192
00:16:50,284 --> 00:16:52,424
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>No, it was skill.</b></font>

193
00:16:52,424 --> 00:16:53,884
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What?</b></font>

194
00:16:53,884 --> 00:16:57,054
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The last corner was downhill,</b></font>

195
00:16:57,054 --> 00:17:01,364
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>so I knew it would come
down to the front tires.</b></font>

196
00:17:01,364 --> 00:17:03,534
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You couldn't quite control them</b></font>

197
00:17:03,534 --> 00:17:06,904
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>because they were too compressed.</b></font>

198
00:17:06,904 --> 00:17:11,644
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I kept up my speed,
but maintained the tire pressure.</b></font>

199
00:17:11,644 --> 00:17:13,934
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It was skill.</b></font>

200
00:17:32,794 --> 00:17:34,994
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You did it, Keisuke!</b></font>

201
00:17:34,994 --> 00:17:36,764
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Should we do a downhill race?</b></font>

202
00:17:36,764 --> 00:17:39,604
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>We can't keep going in this rain.</b></font>

203
00:17:39,604 --> 00:17:41,904
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>--Right.
--Then, Keisuke...</b></font>

204
00:17:41,904 --> 00:17:45,344
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>--...please let me race the Eight-Six.
--What?</b></font>

205
00:17:45,344 --> 00:17:49,674
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>This isn't Akagi or his home course,</b></font>

206
00:17:49,674 --> 00:17:51,414
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>so this is as fair as it gets.</b></font>

207
00:17:51,414 --> 00:17:52,984
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>--Hey.
--Iketani.</b></font>

208
00:17:52,984 --> 00:17:54,814
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Who is he?</b></font>

209
00:17:54,814 --> 00:17:58,344
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>--No idea.
--Kenta!</b></font>

210
00:18:00,184 --> 00:18:02,814
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Takumi Fujiwara, isn't it?</b></font>

211
00:18:04,194 --> 00:18:06,364
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Kenta Nakamura of the Red Suns.</b></font>

212
00:18:06,364 --> 00:18:09,764
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>How about me and you in this rain?</b></font>

213
00:18:09,764 --> 00:18:12,364
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>We gotta talk to my brother first.</b></font>

214
00:18:12,364 --> 00:18:15,204
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Let's ask the spectators, Keisuke.</b></font>

215
00:18:15,204 --> 00:18:19,044
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Wanna see us battle it out in the rain?!</b></font>

216
00:18:19,044 --> 00:18:22,674
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>--Yeah!
--Come on!</b></font>

217
00:18:24,514 --> 00:18:28,014
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>--Darn.
--Hard to say no now.</b></font>

218
00:18:28,014 --> 00:18:32,654
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>But he's racing against
Ryosuke Takahashi next week.</b></font>

219
00:18:32,654 --> 00:18:34,184
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'm first.</b></font>

220
00:18:34,184 --> 00:18:39,864
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>If you can't beat me, you're
certainly not worth Ryosuke's time.</b></font>

221
00:18:39,864 --> 00:18:42,034
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What do you say?</b></font>

222
00:18:42,034 --> 00:18:44,704
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I love racing in the rain.</b></font>

223
00:18:44,704 --> 00:18:48,734
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Don't tell me you're scared of the rain?</b></font>

224
00:18:48,734 --> 00:18:51,374
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>No, not now!</b></font>

225
00:18:51,374 --> 00:18:54,714
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>He hasn't, uh, been himself lately.</b></font>

226
00:18:54,714 --> 00:18:56,714
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Sure, why not?</b></font>

227
00:18:56,714 --> 00:18:59,474
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Wow!</b></font>

228
00:19:04,254 --> 00:19:07,754
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>--Hold it.
--No one can stop it now.</b></font>

229
00:19:07,754 --> 00:19:12,724
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>--But...
--He's not anyone's "private" target.</b></font>

230
00:19:12,724 --> 00:19:16,394
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Every racer wants a piece of him.</b></font>

231
00:19:16,394 --> 00:19:20,564
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I know you understand that feeling.</b></font>

232
00:19:20,564 --> 00:19:22,404
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That's more like it.</b></font>

233
00:19:22,404 --> 00:19:27,004
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Downhill in the rain.
That makes it a pure skill race.</b></font>

234
00:19:27,004 --> 00:19:30,704
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Set your proud Eight-Six next to mine.</b></font>

235
00:19:31,784 --> 00:19:34,444
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>--Let's go, Itsuki.
--I'm going, too?</b></font>

236
00:19:34,444 --> 00:19:39,454
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>If I leave you here, I'll have
to come back up afterwards.</b></font>

237
00:19:39,454 --> 00:19:43,184
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Let's just race down and go straight home.</b></font>

238
00:19:45,394 --> 00:19:47,364
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>So, I'm getting in, then?</b></font>

239
00:19:47,364 --> 00:19:51,204
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Wait, Itsuki, do you mind sitting in the back?</b></font>

240
00:19:51,204 --> 00:19:54,434
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>In the back? Okay, I guess.</b></font>

241
00:19:55,734 --> 00:19:57,904
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Is this a strategy?</b></font>

242
00:19:57,904 --> 00:20:02,744
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Maybe it is... maybe it isn't.</b></font>

243
00:20:02,744 --> 00:20:06,244
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What? You don't know yourself?</b></font>

244
00:20:06,244 --> 00:20:09,114
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>How do I stay seated when you drift?</b></font>

245
00:20:09,114 --> 00:20:12,424
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>--You'll manage.
--What?! Hey!</b></font>

246
00:20:12,424 --> 00:20:16,724
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's only from here to the
bottom of the mountain.</b></font>

247
00:20:16,724 --> 00:20:19,394
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's not over. There's one more race.</b></font>

248
00:20:19,394 --> 00:20:22,624
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I hear Akina's Eight-Six is racing!</b></font>

249
00:20:23,994 --> 00:20:26,604
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>No oncoming traffic!</b></font>

250
00:20:26,604 --> 00:20:28,334
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Let's do this!</b></font>

251
00:20:30,074 --> 00:20:32,404
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I wasn't expecting this.</b></font>

252
00:20:32,404 --> 00:20:35,174
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Yeah. But there's nothing we can do now.</b></font>

253
00:20:35,174 --> 00:20:37,674
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Don't worry, Keisuke.</b></font>

254
00:20:37,674 --> 00:20:39,984
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I like rain.</b></font>

255
00:20:39,984 --> 00:20:44,114
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Before I joined the team,
I purposely waited for rainy days</b></font>

256
00:20:44,114 --> 00:20:48,124
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>to practice my drifting technique.</b></font>

257
00:20:48,124 --> 00:20:51,764
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The rain reduces the wear on the tires.</b></font>

258
00:20:51,764 --> 00:20:55,464
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I see you're confident,
but don't take it lightly.</b></font>

259
00:20:55,464 --> 00:20:58,004
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'm the most experienced in the rain.</b></font>

260
00:20:58,004 --> 00:21:01,704
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I know I'm better than him in the rain,</b></font>

261
00:21:01,704 --> 00:21:05,364
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>because the rain is on my side.</b></font>

262
00:21:09,474 --> 00:21:13,484
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Takumi, you don't look too sharp.</b></font>

263
00:21:13,484 --> 00:21:16,814
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Are you sure you'll be okay in the rain?</b></font>

264
00:21:16,814 --> 00:21:18,324
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Who knows?</b></font>

265
00:21:18,324 --> 00:21:23,024
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I can't go too fast in the rain,
so I'll drive normally.</b></font>

266
00:21:23,024 --> 00:21:26,694
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Who knows if I'll be fast or slow?</b></font>

267
00:21:26,694 --> 00:21:28,694
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'll take it easy,</b></font>

268
00:21:28,694 --> 00:21:32,964
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>'cause if I crashed, my dad would kill me.</b></font>

269
00:21:32,964 --> 00:21:34,694
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That's true.</b></font>

270
00:21:35,904 --> 00:21:40,044
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>But if he loses this race,</i>
<i>there won't be a race against...</i></b></font>

271
00:21:40,044 --> 00:21:42,134
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>...Ryosuke Takahashi!</i></b></font>

272
00:21:43,874 --> 00:21:45,984
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'll count down!</b></font>

273
00:21:45,984 --> 00:21:48,084
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Five... Four...</b></font>

274
00:21:48,084 --> 00:21:50,014
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Three... Two...</b></font>

275
00:21:50,014 --> 00:21:52,514
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>One... Go!</b></font>

276
00:22:04,494 --> 00:22:06,164
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Ouch!</b></font>

277
00:22:19,044 --> 00:22:22,954
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>This isn't... normal!</b></font>

278
00:22:34,524 --> 00:22:40,364
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Ai ni tsukare hate samayotteta koro</i></b></font>

279
00:22:40,364 --> 00:22:48,214
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Yokubou dake ni kararete miushinatteita</i></b></font>

280
00:22:48,214 --> 00:22:54,614
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Kimagure na unmei wa</i></b></font>

281
00:22:54,614 --> 00:23:02,254
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Mujaki na hitomi ni miserarete yuku</i></b></font>

282
00:23:03,624 --> 00:23:10,164
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Sake bara no you ni akaku</i>
<i>tsuyoku, tsuyoku kimi o daite</i></b></font>

283
00:23:10,164 --> 00:23:16,974
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Tatta hitotsu kono omoi o shinjitsu da to ieru</i></b></font>

284
00:23:16,974 --> 00:23:22,144
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Yorokobi o kanadeyou...</i></b></font>

285
00:23:22,144 --> 00:23:29,244
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Kagayaku mirai e</i></b></font>

286
00:23:41,194 --> 00:23:48,874
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Kazoe kirenai hodo tashikame aou</i></b></font>

287
00:23:48,874 --> 00:23:54,944
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Jounetsu yo eien e todoke</i></b></font>

288
00:23:54,944 --> 00:24:01,614
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Sake bara no you ni akaku</i>
<i>tsuyoku, tsuyoku dakishimete</i></b></font>

289
00:24:01,614 --> 00:24:08,454
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Tatoe nani o ushinattemo</i>
<i>kono ude o hanasanai</i></b></font>

290
00:24:08,454 --> 00:24:13,694
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Utsukushiku karen ni sake...</i></b></font>

291
00:24:13,694 --> 00:24:20,064
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Kiseki no hana yo</i></b></font>

292
00:24:26,504 --> 00:24:28,814
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>You seem confident in the rain, Kenta.</i></b></font>

293
00:24:28,814 --> 00:24:30,714
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Yes, I am confident.</i></b></font>

294
00:24:30,714 --> 00:24:34,014
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I'll win because Keisuke is watching me.</i></b></font>

295
00:24:34,014 --> 00:24:36,414
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>But even Keisuke lost to this Eight-Six.</i></b></font>

296
00:24:36,414 --> 00:24:40,384
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I'm avenging that loss! This is for Keisuke.</i></b></font>

297
00:24:40,384 --> 00:24:42,654
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>--This is your first time here...</i>
<i>--No problem!</i></b></font>

298
00:24:42,654 --> 00:24:45,724
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I have to give it my best for Keisuke!</i></b></font>

299
00:24:45,724 --> 00:24:49,264
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Kenta, do you have feelings for Keisuke?</i></b></font>

300
00:24:49,264 --> 00:24:50,694
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I, uh...</i></b></font>

301
00:24:50,694 --> 00:24:53,904
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Next on Initial D: "The Rainy Downhill."</i></b></font>

302
00:24:53,904 --> 00:24:55,664
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Don't miss it!</i></b></font>

